data.description: Hey there, future homeowner! Picture this: a snazzy 3-bed, 1.5-bath row house nestled in the vibrant vibes of Hillcrest Heights. It's the kind of pad that  says come on in stay awhile!' and guess what? It's loaded with perks that'll make your life a breeze!  Curious about the goodies? Well, let’s dive in! Imagine a fully finished basement – we're talking laundry area, a media room perfect for binge-watching, and an extra flex space. Yoga studio by morning, home office by day, or maybe your personal fitness zone – it's your call!  Stroll up to the main level where the hardwood floors shine, and the kitchen's all decked out with modern appliances. There's a dining room for those fancy dinners and a nifty nook that’s waiting for your creative spark – breakfast hideout or artist's  studio or creative space, perhaps?  This gem is ideal for the first-timer who's ready to nest or the savvy simplifier craving space without the hassle. Fancy a yard that's just the right size, complete with a deck to sip your morning brew and storage sheds to tuck away your treasures? It's all here.   The cherry on top? This hotspot is just a hop away from major roads and shopping galore. This home isn't just back with benefits – it's your ticket to the good life. So, what are you waiting for? Lock in that private tour and let's get you into the dream digs that are so much more than just a place to crash. It's home, with a capital 'H'!
